<P>
 University 10, Tustin 6 -- Dan Hayes scored six goals for visiting University, 
which beat the 10th-ranked team in the county. Dave Foley and Ryan Hoff each 
scored twice for Tustin, which played without three starters, who were out 
because of injuries. 
</P>
