Gorky's "The Summer People," translated by Nicholas Saunders and Frank Dwyer 
Feb. 11: an untitled play by Joan Ackermann, 2 p.m. Feb. 11: Robert O'Hara's 
"Insurrection" Feb. 12: Sharon R. Beatty's "Prickly Pears," 2 p.m. Feb. 12: 
